WEBVTT

00:07:29.180 --> 00:07:32.182
Within two minutes of his execution,

00:07:32.206 --> 00:07:34.300
they had given him a stay.

00:07:36.456 --> 00:07:39.631
This stay gave me time

00:07:40.377 --> 00:07:42.081
to reach out to Bobby.

00:07:43.319 --> 00:07:45.460
And as crazy as it may sound,

00:07:45.484 --> 00:07:47.386
we became friends.

00:07:48.936 --> 00:07:50.920
Three months later,

00:07:50.944 --> 00:07:53.786
he was executed
by the State of Mississippi.

00:07:55.415 --> 00:08:00.004
I'm here to tell you my story,